{"type": "article", "id": 28614, "title": "H&M 销售额增速放缓，以及，新的男装秀出炉｜浮华日报", "description": "我们为你挑选了今天最重要和最好看的时尚新闻。\r\n", "date": "2016-06-23T12:17:57Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 24270, "name": "可拆卸肩带"}, {"id": 3786, "name": "包袋"}, {"id": 29333, "name": "男装秀"}, {"id": 2000, "name": "F1"}, {"id": 5264, "name": "童装"}, {"id": 319, "name": "电商"}, {"id": 11592, "name": "夏季"}, {"id": 1531, "name": "帽子"}, {"id": 779, "name": "Prada"}, {"id": 16821, "name": "Vêtements"}, {"id": 29334, "name": "VIBRATE"}, {"id": 7469, "name": "Lemaire"}, {"id": 3203, "name": "Balenciaga"}, {"id": 1653, "name": "Michael Kors"}, {"id": 22016, "name": "Christopher Kane"}, {"id": 1530, "name": "Lanvin"}, {"id": 1060, "name": "H&M"}, {"id": 29335, "name": "Demna Gvasalia"}], "category": 19, "column": 8, "author": 113313, "comment_count": 4, "praise_count": 36, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702170523nMdT86B7GeRE2FkD.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<h2>一些重要的新闻：</h2>\n<p><a href=\"http://wwd.com/markets-news/juniors/lanvin-simonetta-sign-childrens-wear-licensing-agreement-10465421/\"><b>Lanvin 和 Simonetta 签童装协议</b></a>｜ 意大利制造厂商 Simonetta 近日与 Lanvin 签下童装特许权协议，前者可设计、生产和分销新的 Lanvin Enfants 童装产品线。将在 2017 春季首发，包括 3- 24 个月的婴儿以及 2-14 岁的儿童成衣、鞋履。</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://fashionista.com/2016/06/hm-first-half-year-2016\"><b>H&amp;M 销售额增速放缓</b></a>｜H&amp;M 周三发布 2016 上半年财报，归咎于寒春及美元强劲等因素，二季度增长缓慢，CEO Karl-Johan Persson 表示，三四月的销售增长明显低于计划。二季度销售额近增长 5%，三年内最弱表现，利润达 70 亿克朗（约合 8.5 亿美元），相比计划内的 72.3 亿克朗低了不少。</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://m.us.fashionmag.com/news/Christopher-Kane-moves-into-e-commerce,706484.html\"><b>Christopher Kane 推出电商业务</b></a>｜ Christopher Kane 周三推出品牌首个官方电商网站，去年二月 Christopher Kane 在伦敦开设首间实体旗舰店，创意总监 Christopher Kane 本人表示线上网站将是品牌的“全球旗舰店”。网站与奢侈品电商 Farfetch 的 white-label 电商平台 Black &amp; White 合作。</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://m.us.fashionmag.com/news/Michael-Kors-announces-new-Formula-1-partnership-with-McLaren-Honda,706547.html\"><b>Michael Kors 宣布与 F1 强队迈凯轮合作</b></a>｜Michael Kors 近日宣布与 F1 冠军车队迈凯轮（McLaren-Honda）合作，成为后者生活方式层面的搭档。MK 认为品牌的快速、乘喷气飞机环游世界的生活方式与 F1 很搭，此次合作有助于男装品类在欧洲的增长。MK 的品牌标识将出现在车手的工装裤以及迈凯轮 MP4-31 赛车上。为庆祝合作， Michael Kors 在伦敦旗舰店上新了男士机车皮夹克，限量 50 件。</p>\n<p class=\"\"><a href=\"http://www.dazeddigital.com/fashion/article/31700/1/cindy-crawford-s-daughter-kaia-stars-in-new-miu-miu-film\"><b>Cindy Crawford 女儿出镜 Miu Miu 新广告</b></a>｜传奇超模 Cindy Crawford  的 14 女儿 Kaia Gerber ，近日单独为 Miu Miu 眼镜系列拍摄广告影片。<br></p>\n<p class=\"\"></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021704556nWJxT9VEjFUgsy2.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.58142494\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><p></p>\n<h2>一些值得一看的：</h2>\n<p class=\"\">Prada 新一季包袋也用上了可拆卸肩带，花朵点缀。此前<a href=\"http://www.qdaily.com/articles/23118.html\">我们还介绍过 Fendi 推出的肩带</a>。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021704560velBxRk76MFwc8X.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">Prada</div></figcaption></figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702170456uFif0jeZyW2p8MEw.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">Prada</div></figcaption></figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702170457CMYDp70dik9xPt4X.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">Prada</div></figcaption></figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702170457YpQ1XjgwPAkNGnVO.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">Prada</div></figcaption></figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/2016070217045874G62hpjfPaNYEMW.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">Prada</div></figcaption></figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702170459C2Vw6yDGgRvkE0th.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66574074\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">Prada</div></figcaption></figure>\n</div>\n<p class=\"\"></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702170459hCEWiyoeYHJPAZaB.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><p></p>\n<p class=\"\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><i>Fendi</i></p>\n<p>Demna Gvasalia 执掌的<a href=\"http://wwd.com/runway/mens-spring-collections-2017/paris/valentino/review/\"> Balenciaga 2017 春夏男装秀</a>在巴黎落幕，这是 Balenciaga 首次举办单独的男装秀。耸起的方正垫肩，略眼熟：</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<p></p>\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702170500cSO9ubXqwpWs7gEx.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.54166667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702170500ixRzqc4ykDQM2dAV.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75185185\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702170501VY1dqUwcCWmu5kOR.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75185185\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702170501XgQ6qN9GEalfFZxH.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75185185\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702170502DWZF0bgUMkA7l16L.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75185185\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/2016070217050281MpJsFVdCZ47qxI.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75185185\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<p>Valentino 发布 <a href=\"http://wwd.com/runway/mens-spring-collections-2017/paris/valentino/review/\">2017 春夏男装系列</a>：</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<p></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702170503y7tixENR6Gr1paSJ.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75185185\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702170503ngYfLuC81aqzhiIF.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75185185\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021705044OrEyXh2i8GTR95U.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75185185\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021705042t7UZRDN1kEecFVW.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75185185\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702170505cD5PLkfTSXKUHmh6.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75185185\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021705050MUeh7G5wsnWH8SA.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75185185\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702170506nu3BmXbkjOg7LhiS.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75185185\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<p class=\"\"><a href=\"http://hypebeast.com/2016/6/lemaire-ss17\">Lemaire 的 2017 春夏男装系列</a>，带有很多口袋、夹层的风衣和外套搭配皮鞋、布鞋看起来很实穿：<br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<p></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702170506gnX8eZKofJkLs30b.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75498008\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702170507xCHbog7JwWOKqXcT.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75498008\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702170508X2Jui1k4Ms7DC6IV.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75498008\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src