"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702170514BdqczhyGtSU1m0Ax.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66707317\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702170515ABR8VNKuDfh6dj4T.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66707317\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702170516LJmze2GDOYpaudyo.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66707317\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702170516sRou4CiMvpglhbN3.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66707317\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702170517gqwet1Nnfm8FcD9s.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66707317\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<p class=\"\">前文提到 Balenciaga 创意总监  Demna Gvasalia，他作为设计师的另一品牌 <a href=\"http://hypebeast.com/2016/6/vetements-2016-fall-winter-collection-lookbook-will-be-arriving-at-dover-street-market-tomorrow\">Vetements 也发布了 2016 秋冬系列 lookbook</a>：</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<p></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021705183q4rVawCJ0Ec6NMx.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.68981481\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702170518p7FEgBY30jDWIzKk.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.68981481\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702170519nRO6U9LQ7H2eP1Ja.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.68981481\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702170519eGPosBR5CIl3krWU.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.68981481\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021705202tb1FVEQWXNvL56e.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.68981481\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702170520CsNPguMW4wHtkFoV.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.68981481\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702170521CdOqYbJlsGRFHc8X.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.68981481\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702170521jgCIVpQZzouKkyAi.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.68981481\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702170522EF5u493RJZkC0Dct.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.68981481\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<p class=\"\"><br></p>\n\n"}